50|$|Simmonds {{joined the}} Royal Canadian Mounted Police on April 23, 1947 where he trained at “Depot” Division in Regina. The {{following}} year, while touring with the RCMP Musical Ride, he performed <b>highway</b> <b>patrols</b> in Edmonton. He was subsequently posted to “K” Division, serving Edmonton, Innisfail, Three Hills, Wetaskiwin, Hanna and Calgary.|$|R
